						<summary>

						<p>It records gift of one <hi rend="italic">achchu</hi> by one Jayasiṅgadēvaṉ perumān <hi rend="italic">alias</hi> Aḻagiyapāṇḍyadēvaṉ for burning a twilight lamp to the god at Tirumurugaṉpūṇḍi. The Śivabrāhmaṇas of the temple received the gift and agreed to burn the lamp.</p>						

